data.description: This Cape Cod style beach house offers the Florida lifestyle without the stress of high maintenance or fees. Nestled between the Ocean & River you'll enjoy endless opportunities to soak up the sun, comb the beach, surf, fish, kayak & view sea turtle nesting. Inside you are greeted by a bright & inviting atmosphere with luxury laminate flooring that adds warmth & elegance to the coastal feel. Updates include new flooring, kitchen w/granite counters, beautiful custom cabinets & new Wind Rated Windows. Stunning landscaping finishes your tropical island paradise. A simply fantastic neighborhood, lies between the Ocean & the Indian River. Residents enjoy sunrises, sunsets, & Pickleball in the street.
